# Vercel Platform

- Feature flags required for risky rollouts
- Cron jobs idempotent + observable
- Vercel Observability used by default
- Default runtime: Node.js
- Edge runtime requires ADR justification in `docs/adr/`
- Environment variables in Vercel dashboard
- Automatic deployments from `main` branch
- Preview deployments from pull requests
- Use Vercel defaults unless justified
- Cron jobs: Use Vercel Cron (configure in `vercel.json`)
- Analytics: Use Vercel Analytics and Speed Insights
